	  refactor: &define_verbose_var: accept a third optional argument

2012-06-14  Stefano Lattarini  <stefano.lattarini@gmail.com>

	tests: minor reorganization of few tests

	* t/subdir3.sh: Rename ...
	* t/sourcefile-in-subdir.sh: ... like this.
