	* configure.ac (AC_INIT): Bump version number to 1.11e, as per
	HACKING suggestion.
	* NEWS: Likewise.
	* m4/amversion.m4: Likewise (autoupdated by ./bootstrap).

2012-04-18  Stefano Lattarini  <stefano.lattarini@gmail.com>

