	* doc/automake.texi (Using the TAP test protocol): Here ...
	* tests/tap-doc2.test: ... and here.

2012-03-24  Stefano Lattarini  <stefano.lattarini@gmail.com>

	build: remove duplicated entries in $(TESTS)

